OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Halt Ofsted inspections   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter my sister's death'   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Pausing Ofsted inspections would be the
OL,6, "empathetic, human, correct thing to   
OL,7, do", says the sister of a head teacher 
OL,8, who took her own life after an         
OL,9, inspection - as the watchdog announces 
OL,10, some changes to how it works.          
OL,12,FRuth Perry died while waiting for a    
OL,13,Freport that downgraded her school.     
OL,15,FHer sister, Prof Julia Waters, wants a 
OL,16,Ffull review to take place.             
OL,18,FOfsted is making some changes, such as 
OL,19,Fhow it manages complaints - but will   
OL,20,Fkeep its one-word grading system.      
